biography: Say “Beembo!” We are the largest baking company in the country, bringing you America's most iconic bread and sweet baked goods brands. #BBUPROUD 🍞💙

latestIgtvVideos.caption: Happy Earth Day from Bimbo Bakeries USA! Over the past week, you’ve gotten a chance to see how BBU continues to Nourish A Better World, now we get a chance to hear from a few of our associates about what they do in their daily lives to help preserve the planet. #BBUPROUD

‼ New Product Alert ‼ Introducing NEW Sara Lee White Bread Made with Veggies: baked with the equivalent of one cup of vegetables per loaf. It’s also made with added vitamins A, D and E for an easy and tasty way to add more nutrients to you and your family’s meals. Available now!

Last month, we launched #BBUPROUD Days, a two-week event to recognize the hard work and commitment of all our BBU associates. Teams across the country gathered at their locations and celebrated the dedication and passion of our associates through team events, lunches, raffles, family fun days, giveaways and more! #BBUPROUD
To close out our 2022 Hispanic Heritage Month celebration, our associate Alexander Peraza, Market Sales Leader, shares his Hispanic culture with us! #YouBelong

On this episode of #BBUPROUD – Mission: Recognition, hear our associates at the Commerce City, CO Sales Center pick and choose their favorite Bimbo Bakeries USA products… and even hear which product they think is the most underrated! 🥪🍪 #BBUPROUD
Happy National Hispanic Heritage Month! Bimbo Bakeries USA Customer Manager Gabriella Ponce shares her Hispanic culture with us. Check it out! #HispanicHeritageMonth2022 #YouBelong

BBU recently opened their reimagined headquarters space in Horsham, PA. Tune in to this episode of the #BBUPROUD Video Series to check out the renovated facility and how it will help enable BBU’s Balanced Approach to work! The unique space will nourish connection, flexibility and the wellbeing of our associates. #BBUPROUD
Happy First Day of Fall! What better way to ring in the season than with a festive treat! Try limited edition Pumpkin @littlebitessnacks for all the fall feels. 🎃🍂

WE'RE BACK! It's been long awaited, but today we present you with season 3 of the #BBUPROUD video series – Mission: Recognition! This season will recognize the great work that our associates do every day and the facilities they work at nationwide. Check out the first episode highlighting our Grand Rapids, MI Bakery and our company culture! 💙🍞

Sign up with your family and friends for our LA live race event on 9/25. Run a 5K or 10K, then enjoy our finish line festival featuring live music, kids zones and more. Register now at the link in our bio! #YouRunWeDonate

Bimbo Bakeries USA is committed to giving back to the communities where we live and work! We recognize our role in being a force of good in the world and are dedicated to making positive changes in our society. 💙🍞 #BBUPROUD
